
Flash translation layer
Limitation 1 : Erase-before-write
Limitation 2 : Flash can be written in pages but can only be erased as a Block of pages
Limitation 3 : Flash can be ”Read“ or ”Written” only for a certain number of times

Multi-channel  NVMe
Implementation of READ,WRITE and DELETE- partly done


Parallelism in NVme
There may be multiple commands outstanding to different LUNs at the same time. To get further parallelism within a LUN,
multi-plane operations may be used to execute additional dependent operations in parallel

